==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blackness
<hw>Black"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
black; black color; atrociousness or enormity in wickedness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They're darker now than <qex>blackness</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Donne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>blackout</ent>⟦br⟧
